Nevves sent to the Ladie Princesse of Orenge. Translated out of French into English by I.E. Eliot, John, attributed name.
[8] p.
Printed by Iohn VVolfe, London : 1589.
A translation, possibly by John Eliot, from the original French. "The Ladie Princesse of Orenge" = Louise de Coligny, widow of William I.--Cf. STC. Signatures: A⁴. Reproduction of the original in the Peterborough Cathedral Library.
